    "body": "I’m on pop-os (based on ubuntu 22.04) so I have [`fish version 3.3.1`](https://fishshell.com/docs/3.3/cmds/set.html) and `starship 1.24.1` (installed with `cargo`).\n\nI do not have the \"1m25s\" issue, but I have the `set: Unknown -f option`\n\nI just tried disabling the [jobs](https://starship.rs/config/#jobs) module since logs point to there, but I still have the errors on screen.\n```toml\n[jobs]\ndisabled = true\n```",
